{"tid":1392963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑：解放軍出兵香港，必定引發第三次世界大戰","createTime":"2019-08-01T02:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T09:49:27.000Z","uid":1002,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a62c215c93a2fcfcf4feb6ce2d86cc3942e888f0","tid":1392963,"uid":1002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:27:20.000Z","msg":"中國國防部發言人以朗誦的腔調，引用「駐軍法」，鏗鏘宣布：若香港特區政府提出要求，中國會出動解放軍維持香港社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n這句話，要點在於「特區政府提出要求」。因為基本法第六條和第十八條，雖然都提到香港宣佈進入「緊急狀態」，主詞比較曖昧，要仔細看，才領會得到是人大常委會單方面決定香港不行了，特區政府管不了，香港出現了危害國家領土統一的狀況了，由人大常委會單方面宣佈香港進入緊急狀態。<br />\n<br />\n換言之，這次是中國方面比較清晰地告訴美國：解放軍在手續上，是要林鄭楚楚可憐地提出要求，才會出軍營。中方不會主動。<br />\n<br />\n有人說：林鄭那時會有說不請求出兵的自主嗎？這個問題，也沒有絕對。香港到底是國際城市，中國需要香港這條熱錢的進出渠道。林鄭不是自己人，中國不會相信她。若她受到有力人士脅迫，解放軍放出來，國際傳媒鏡頭集中在林鄭身上。在記者逼問之下，壓力太大，林鄭梨花帶雨，「哇」的一聲哭出來，說：「不是我的主意。是有人用一根杖抵着我的腰肢，叫我唸台詞的。」這樣國家就比較被動。<br />\n<br />\n所以，香港會不會有解放軍出動？環球時報才子主筆胡錫進，是最清醒的一個，斬釘截鐵說「使不得」：除非出現親中愛國人士，大量慘遭黃絲和泛民屠殺，紛紛北逃大陸，國家不得已，解放軍才會出來保護愛國同胞。<br />\n<br />\n黃絲和泛民，哪來的膽識和武器，對香港愛國同胞展開血腥大屠殺？只有一個可能，就是當美軍已經先登陸，向他們派發槍枝武器。<br />\n<br />\n在香港出解放軍，有非常複雜的機制。不是怕了美國，而是美帝的因素必須考慮。<br />\n<br />\n譬如美國天經地義，說要撤僑，由菲律賓和關島，派出兩艘航空母艦、率領十艘八隻戰艦，開來香港，幾十萬香港的年輕人歡呼：美國來解放我們了。那時只解放軍在城中屠殺黑衫年輕人，沒有用，還要出動海軍，在香港海域外攔截美國戰艦。<br />\n<br />\n那時會怎麼樣？必然第三次世界大戰。解放軍出兵，蝴蝶效應，可能導致洛杉磯和中國幾個城市在核襲中一齊毀滅。這只是軍事學的常識。然而，林鄭一手搞出如此大場面，終究是創造了歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陶傑/daily/article/20190726/20737270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B6%E5%82%91%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190726%2F20737270&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGOQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=4bd789d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B6%E5%82%91%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190726%2F20737270&h=4a01a002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陶傑/daily/article/20190726/20737270</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利害了，共匪國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"29634c8a4572785c642799385a03af76d25106d1","tid":1392963,"uid":51814,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:29:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老解出兵會否第一時間凍結銀行户口？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dtRugS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dtRugS</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>仲慘過雷曼爆煲！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"dd522370469a748957e9d37982f35142b56590b4","tid":1392963,"uid":282718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:30:31.000Z","msg":"願所有香港人都有一顆強壯既心<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6a4d7b1bdab59820f1c3eaf744e8ca76dbef522e","tid":1392963,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:11:31.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"5991dd4c88dca32db5384cc322e30fe2dc86f386","tid":1392963,"uid":32502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:13:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n來吧<br />\n反正冇野輸"},{"pid":"8d107304777600e95072a6b506edfd620571497f","tid":1392963,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:16:14.000Z","msg":"莫道林病大細眼<br />\n<br />\n挑動送中天下反"},{"pid":"840f1e8ee124cd2a954ac238483c501a8d253502","tid":1392963,"uid":287411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"推L到支那出兵"},{"pid":"b00420f2df4d34dfc8a2c017eb38b76747904e12","tid":1392963,"uid":38204,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:17:41.000Z","msg":"估唔到有身之年可以有呢啲大場面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔出解放軍正契弟</span></span>"},{"pid":"29cf05ffddce56fb2ba9e04a34081128382b07b5","tid":1392963,"uid":274680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:18:19.000Z","msg":"太好了，香港人輸出ww3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c20505e3681b5d2c96f69a4c758a6b88b776bf","tid":1392963,"uid":270307,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:20:34.000Z","msg":"估唔到第三次世界大戰事源2個MK仔中出MK妹<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8689d90504e274707ed8f4a37b978c63e704cf4a","tid":1392963,"uid":27194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:22:58.000Z","msg":"香港年輕人唔會講 美軍來解放我們了！<br />\n<br />\n我地會講 sir, this way.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11de7928bd393aa84f0990b6791205fc153656e","tid":1392963,"uid":237462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:30:01.000Z","msg":"支持解放軍光復香港<br />\n引發三次大戰<br />\n歷史留名2個MK<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n極力支持解放軍來港清洗<br />\n大家一齊攬炒<br />\n外資撒走<br />\n建立大灣區共榮圈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{